{"tid":1595835,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"超猛！61歲阿嬤替兒代孕 自己的孫女自己生","createTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T13:16:23.000Z","uid":225846,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"02e17c84b9cb1517a2aab97349bb98a2220ef1e9","tid":1595835,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/01/realtime/6121719.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F01%2Frealtime%2F6121719.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=2ee84845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國內布拉斯加州一名61歲婦女希瑟利（Cecile Eledge）為兒子擔任代理孕母，並於上月25日產下親生孫女。翻攝自CNN<br />\n<br />\n美國內布拉斯加州一名61歲婦女希瑟利（Cecile Eledge）替兒子擔任代理孕母，於上月25日順利誕下自己的親生孫女。<br />\n<br />\n希瑟利的32歲兒子艾利傑（Matthew Eledge）是同志，他和29歲的丈夫多亨特（Elliot Dougherty）始終渴望擁有自己的孩子，希瑟利得知後，便主動提出自己能作為代理孕母，並說這還能省下一大筆錢。希瑟利告訴KETV-News，「我沒有猶豫片刻，這是天生的本能」。<br />\n<br />\n希瑟利在經過全套身體檢查後，奧瑪哈大學內布拉斯加州醫學中心予以批准，發現希瑟利的身體狀況可以勝任代孕母親的角色。<br />\n<br />\n希瑟利先經過一系列激素治療，接著醫生用艾利傑的精子和多亨特妹妹的卵子結合成的受精卵，植入希瑟利體內。幸運的是第一次植入時，希瑟利就成功受孕。<br />\n<br />\n上月25日，希瑟利誕下一名重5磅13盎司（約2635克）的女嬰Uma。醫生說原以為希瑟利需要接受剖腹產，沒想到她憑藉自己力量，產下女嬰。<br />\n<br />\n希瑟利和艾利傑在法律上都是Uma的父母，因為內布拉斯加州要求代理孕母必須被列為母親，所以Uma既是希瑟利的孫女，也是女兒。<br />\n<br />\n艾利傑表示，「如果你是同性戀並且已經結婚，然後想要小孩，你就會知道你必須以特殊的方式建立家庭」。<br />\n<br />\n艾利傑對母親無私的奉獻行為感到十分感激和尊重，「Uma的出生把全家人聚集在一起，我母親是一位了不起的女人，這經歷很特別，感謝Uma和母親都健康平安」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/01/realtime/6121718.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F01%2Frealtime%2F6121718.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=e1765f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希瑟利的32歲兒子艾利傑（Matthew Eledge）和29歲的丈夫多亨特（Elliot Dougherty）相當渴望擁有孩子。翻攝自CNN<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/01/realtime/6121720.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F01%2Frealtime%2F6121720.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=4fd38576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上月25日，希瑟利成功誕下一名重5磅13盎司（約2635克）的女嬰Uma。翻攝自獨立報"},{"pid":"aa7314b0cb166fddb4a24f29f84be5b101d6a61e","tid":1595835,"uid":47789,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"gilf <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647528f0875910ed05ea02d3d25d813e13430653","tid":1595835,"uid":258566,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f8bec9406eaa2bc2c9416ec9099ccea3afa58ff","tid":1595835,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7314b0cb166fddb4a24f29f84be5b101d6a61e","tid":1595835,"uid":47789,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"gilf <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"好亂呀！！！！"},{"pid":"11b90e6a9bd891cf73c8fd4fb7b9ecec416bb5e3","tid":1595835,"uid":225846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"647528f0875910ed05ea02d3d25d813e13430653","tid":1595835,"uid":258566,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"你有經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946ce8581f52da9a592fc63d417f821203ed016f","tid":1595835,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f7df38ea24cbf3700d33